channel.title: Someone w/ Teamviewer
channel.description: I would appreciate if someone could help me make my own server. I have source and client and I've switched everything out with my name and no-ip.biz name. I am also port-forwarding. I have set up a static NAT. And I get: No response from server. Please try using a different world. I just thought it would be simpler if you had teamviewer to see what it going on whenever I try doing suggested ways of fixing. And yes I have a port set up on firewall to let it through.
